imdb.plot outline: Anarchist scientist Grant McKay has punched a hole through the barriers between dimensions, allowing travel to all possible universes. But now Grant and his team are trapped in the folds of infinity, careening through a million universes of unimaginable adventure, sanity-flaying danger and no way home.
